---
import {getCollection} from "astro:content";
import Layout from "/src/layouts/Layout.astro";

const allExams=await getCollection("exams");
---

<Layout pageTitle="首页">
	<section class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-white to-sky-50 p-8 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-800 dark:from-slate-900 dark:via-slate-900 dark:to-slate-950">
		<p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300">BYR Docs</p>
		<h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-950 dark:text-white">欢迎来到维基真题</h1>
		<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">本站收录北京邮电大学近年的期中、期末考试题，现有 <span class="font-semibold text-slate-950 dark:text-white">{allExams.length}</span> 篇真题。</p>
		<p class="max-w-3xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">你可以为本站添加试卷、补充题目或撰写解答。任何一笔小编辑都可能帮到无数读者。</p>
	</section>

	<section class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
		<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900">
			<p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">搜索试题</p>
			<h2 class="mt-2 border-none p-0 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-950 dark:text-white">从主站检索真题</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">请使用 BYR Docs 主站的搜索能力按课程名、学期或关键词查找试题。</p>
			<a class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-slate-950 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white no-underline transition hover:bg-slate-800 dark:bg-white dark:text-slate-950 dark:hover:bg-slate-200" href="https://byrdocs.org">打开 BYR Docs</a>
		</div>
		<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900">
			<p class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">作出贡献</p>
			<h2 class="mt-2 border-none p-0 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-950 dark:text-white">编辑试题与解答</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">你可以在 GitHub 仓库中编辑试卷、补充答案并提交 PR。不要担心犯错，持续的小改动同样有价值。</p>
			<a class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 no-underline transition hover:border-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-600 dark:hover:bg-slate-800" href="https://github.com/byrdocs/byrdocs-wiki-internal">查看仓库</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
